g.text: Design Top K most viewed videos service
The user should be able to
1. query the most viewed videos based on "K" (arbitrary number < 1000)
2. time window (hourly, daily, weekly, monthly, all-time)
- no approx. for calculating top K most viewed videos (approx. idea later)
- (fault-tolerant) resume the processing progress even after the system crashs
- video uploaded -> top K most viewed system (<= 60s)
